        "w": 12,
        "x": 12,
        "y": 14
      },
      "options": {
        "content": "\n<div style=\"padding: 15px; background: #e3f2fd; border-radius: 5px;\">\n  <h4>\ud83d\udcca Grafana - Role mapping:</h4>\n  <p><strong>Via Authentik OAuth config:</strong></p>\n  <pre style=\"background: #f5f5f5; padding: 10px; border-radius: 3px;\">\nGroup: Grafana Admins\n  \u2192 Grafana Role: Admin\n  \nGroup: Grafana Users\n  \u2192 Grafana Role: Viewer\n  </pre>\n  \n  <h4>\u2699\ufe0f Configura\u00e7\u00e3o em Grafana:</h4>\n  <p><code>Admin \u2192 Configuration \u2192 OAuth \u2192 Generic Oauth</code></p>\n  <p>Role mapping JMESPath: \n    <code>groups[0]</code></p>\n</div>\n"
      }
    }
